OL,3,CSummerland families 'encouraged' after
OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FCampaigners calling for a fresh
OL,7,Finquest into the Summerland fire say
OL,8,Fthey are 'very encouraged', following
OL,9,Fa meeting with Mayor of Greater
OL,10,FManchester, Andy Burnham.
OL,12,FThe 'Justice for Summerland' campaign
OL,13,Fis calling for a fresh inquest into
OL,14,Fthe fire that killed 50 people, and
OL,15,Finjured many more on the Isle of Man
OL,16,Fin 1973.
OL,18,FMembers of the campaign met with Andy
OL,19,FBurnham on Monday 1 September, hoping
OL,20,Fhe would join the existing political
OL,21,Fsupport for a new inquest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
