OL,3,CSummerland families 'encouraged' after
OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMr Burnham has been a vocal advocate
OL,7,Ffor the Hillsborough families,
OL,8,Fcampaigning with those fighting for
OL,9,Fjustice around the fatal crowd crush
OL,10,Fin 1989.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the meeting, Summerland
OL,13,Fsurvivor Jackie Hallam said: "There
OL,14,Fwere a few bereaved family members at
OL,15,Fthe meeting and listening to our
OL,16,Fstories, we really thought he was
OL,17,Fgetting behind us then.
OL,19,F"He really listened intently and he
OL,20,Fwas very supportive of our plight, he
OL,21,Fwas very encouraging indeed".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
