OL,3,CSummerland families 'encouraged' after
OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FCampaigners had submitted an
OL,7,Fapplication to open a new inquest into
OL,8,Fthe fire earlier this year, however
OL,9,Fthis was subsequently declined by the
OL,10,FIsle of Man Attorney General.
OL,12,FLed by the lawyers representing the
OL,13,Ffamilies, the campaign is planning to
OL,14,Fappeal the decision made by Walter
OL,15,FWannenburgh.
OL,17,FA 'petition of doleance' has been
OL,18,Flodged by the group, which is awaiting
OL,19,Fapproval from the Isle of Man Courts
OL,20,Fof Justice, before an official appeal
OL,21,Fcan be submitted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
