OL,3,CSummerland families 'encouraged' after
OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FJackie said she hoped the Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral would review his decision to
OL,8,Fdeny the families a fresh inquest.
OL,10,FShe said: "I would say to the Attorney
OL,11,FGeneral that you can still write the
OL,12,Fwrongs of the past. All we are seeking
OL,13,Fis truth and justice for our loved
OL,14,Fones, so please give us a chance to be
OL,15,Fheard by putting an end to this court
OL,16,Fprocess, and granting a new inquest."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
