OL,3,CSummerland families 'encouraged' after
OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man Government was also
OL,7,Fcontacted, and released a written
OL,8,Fstatement which read: "The Summerland
OL,9,Ffire leaves a deep and lasting legacy
OL,10,Fon the Isle of Man's recent history
OL,11,Fand across our community to the
OL,12,Fpresent day.
OL,14,F"The Isle of Man Government is
OL,15,Fgrateful for the opportunity to
OL,16,Fcomment. However, as any challenge to
OL,17,Fthe Attorney General's independent
OL,18,Fruling is subject to established legal
OL,19,Fprocedure, it would be inappropriate
OL,20,Fto do so prior to the Court making any
OL,21,Fdetermination."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
