OL,4,Cmeeting with Andy Burnham
OL,6,FCampaigners now await to hear from the
OL,7,FIsle of Man Courts of Justice, to
OL,8,Fconfirm their petition of doleance has
OL,9,Fbeen successful.
OL,11,FAndy Burnham has also been contacted
OL,12,Ffor further comment.
